query:
UPDATE program p
            SET modification_date_time = now(),
                program_name = $2,
                interval_period = $3,
                program_descriptions = $4,
                payload_descriptors = $5,
                targets = $6,
                attributes = $7
            WHERE id = $1
            RETURNING p.id,
                   p.created_date_time,
                   p.modification_date_time,
                   p.program_name,
                   p.interval_period,
                   p.program_descriptions,
                   p.payload_descriptors,
                   p.targets as "targets:Vec<Target>",
                   p.attributes
